dct_title_s: Map of Upper Maumee and Lower Auglaize River Basins showing availability of underground water
dct_alternative_sm: Ohio water plan inventory. Underground water resources. Upper Maumee and Lower Auglaize River Basins
dct_description_sm: Map side also contains legend and explanation of map symbols.
Text includes information about generalized stratigraphic sequence of the rocks in the Upper Maumee and Lower Auglaize Basins, quality of underground water, and summary.
"Prepared by ALFRED C. WALKER, Geologist, Ohio Division of Water, from data compiled by Lawrence R. Brunstetter".
